Boiled eggs

Get water boiling first. Enough to cover all your eggs.

Drop in your eggs carefully. Easy to break. Lower with spoon?

Cover and time :
7 min soft to
10 hard.
11 for making deviled eggs.

Set up bowl of ice water, big enough for all the eggs.
Carefully place all the eggs in the ice bath.

Before they are all cool, peel them under running tap water.

And there you go.